Mathieu van der Poel is a 30-year-old professional cyclist from Netherlands, born January 19th 1995. He rides for Alpecin-Deceuninck, a UCI WorldTeam. He has won 56 UCI races, and is currently ranked 4th in the UCI Ranking. Strengths: Cobbles, Flat, Hilly, Time Trial.
